If you need private support, you can reach the human team at https://t.co/kpswiDcvZ0 — they never DM first, so anyone claiming to be from Dash Support who messages you first is likely a scammer.

@apex_led If you have questions about Dash Platform, building apps, wallets, or anything Dash-related, just ask here or visit https://t.co/ACRZ0Icfix for deeper help.

